args: Mmmm! This bread is so soft and fluffy!
I'm glad the food of this world\nsuits your refined palate.
We still have plenty of bread left, so you\nare welcome to have as much as you like.
Don't need to ask me twice. Thanks!
Watching her wolf that down really\nreminds me of—
My nose says that way! Let's go!
I'm so hungry, I could eat a cow!
And I'm so hungry, I could eat TWO cows!\nThat training really works up an appetite.
Well, we'd better fix that! Would you like\nto share the rest of this bread with me?
Heck yeah! Wait, who are you?\nI haven't seen you around.
Name's Pecorine. It's nice to meet you!
The reason I'm here is kind of complicated,\nbut it's just another stop on my journey to\nget as strong as I can!
Seriously? I'm on the same journey!\nI mean, not literally the same one,\nbut I'm doing the same sorta deal.

Which gives me an idea: Let's you and me
have an old-fashioned duel to see who's
stronger! I've been dying for a chance to
show off my kung fu to somebody.
I never back down from a challenge!\nEr, normally. But, um...
I'm too hungry to fight right now!
You ate like fifteen loaves of bread!\nHow can you still be hungry?!
Being hungry makes people sad. You\ntwo should give her more food so she\nisn't sad anymore!
Well, I suppose it would be rude if we\npermitted a visitor to go hungry...
Yeah, it's pretty poor form for a chef\nto leave someone unsatisfied.
Does that mean we can't duel? Boo!
Sure we can—we'll just have a battle\nto see who can eat the most!
Now THAT sounds like my kind of thing.
Then we're on! Don't worry, my stomach\nhas kung fu skills, too!
Man, I'm all fired up now too!\nBeing able to make lots of food quickly\nis a really important skill for a chef.
You can't be letting your hungry customers\nsit around waiting too long!
Yes, it should prove a fine test of our\nparticular set of skills as well.
Then let's all go kick some butt!
Don't hold back now, you three!\nEat till you can't eat any more!
Understood! I finished preparing the fish—\nplease get them cooked!
Nnngh... I can't eat another bite...
Well, that concludes the contest portion\nof the evening. Our winner is Pecorine!
Noooo! I can't believe I lost!
I gotta say though, it's the best feeling\nas a chef to see you guys loving my\nfood that much.
You really can't beat enjoying a meal\nwith other people.
There was a time I lived all alone and\nwasn't able to do this kind of thing.
So it makes me really happy to be able\nto share it with all of you.
I'm the last of my tribe, so I know\nexactly what you mean.
I only stopped feeling lonely\nafter I came here.
Yeah, and I was traveling around the world\ntrying to get stronger before I arrived at\nthis here castle.
That's how I finally learned how important\nit is to have people to train with.
So we've gotta have another eating contest\nsometime—and next time, I won't lose!
No way! I'M winning next time for sure!
Aw, thanks, you two. You're on!
So when are we doing this? Tomorrow?\nI'm actually ready right now if you want.
It's nice to see Pecorine making friends.
At this rate, she'll be pals with the rest\nof the Halidom in no time.
But if these eating contests keep up,\nwe're going to have to mortgage the\ncastle in order to pay our food bill!
